def_cn: (通过考试)取得资格的，有资格的，合格的
def_en: Someone who is qualified has passed the examinations that they need to pass in order to work in a particular profession.

def_cn: （支持、赞同）有限度的，有保留的
def_en: If you give someone or something qualified support or approval, your support or approval is not total because you have some doubts.
If you describe something as a qualified success, you mean that it is only partly successful.
